commit.message: Support for fused types in cdef functions
Disallow private types in public or api cdef functions
Fix compiler crash with type inferencing and add all() and any() to Utils
Support sharing of cdef functions with fused types
Allow type checks on fused types
Constant fold fused type check expressions with branch pruning
Disallow use of unspecialized fused types
Support casting and assignment of fused functions to specialized functions
Allow indexing of fused cdef functions
Support optional fused-typed arguments in cdef functions
Merge fused cdef functions with master
